            <title>[HBASE-8174] Backport HBASE-8161(setting blocking file count on table level doesn&apos;t work) to 0.94</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-8174</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently, the blocking file count &quot;hbase.hstore.blockingStoreFiles&quot; is configured at region server level.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We should allow it to be configured at Table level.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
