                            <comment id="13609950" author="clockfly" created="Fri, 22 Mar 2013 05:12:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Add patch for 0.94/&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13609971" author="anoopsamjohn" created="Fri, 22 Mar 2013 05:53:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Dont you get the same global config object from region.getConf()? &lt;br/&gt;
Pls see the code in HRegion#setHTableSpecificConf()&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;How you plan to pass the table specific blockingStoreFiles count? Setting as a metadata using setValue()?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13610010" author="clockfly" created="Fri, 22 Mar 2013 07:21:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi Anoop, &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I neglected this, it depends on &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-5335&quot; title=&quot;Dynamic Schema Configurations&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-5335&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-5335&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. I will do a backport of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-5335&quot; title=&quot;Dynamic Schema Configurations&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-5335&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-5335&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; to 0.94.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13610011" author="clockfly" created="Fri, 22 Mar 2013 07:22:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;In HBase-5335, the HRegion will get a compound configuration of regionserver + HTableDescriptor.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13611013" author="sershe" created="Fri, 22 Mar 2013 18:10:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It still may not work though, see &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-8161&quot; title=&quot;setting blocking file count on table level doesn&amp;#39;t work&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-8161&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-8161&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. MemStoreFlusher doesn&apos;t get aggregate config.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13611640" author="clockfly" created="Sat, 23 Mar 2013 06:35:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;@Sergey, yes, your patch is more decent, it is at column family level. Mine only works at Region level.&lt;br/&gt;
Is it worth the risk to backport &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-8161&quot; title=&quot;setting blocking file count on table level doesn&amp;#39;t work&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-8161&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-8161&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-5335&quot; title=&quot;Dynamic Schema Configurations&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-5335&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-5335&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; into 0.94?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13617980" author="lhofhansl" created="Sat, 30 Mar 2013 04:10:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;So this becomes a backport of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-8161&quot; title=&quot;setting blocking file count on table level doesn&amp;#39;t work&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-8161&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-8161&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;? That patch is nice and simple. +1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13618754" author="clockfly" created="Mon, 1 Apr 2013 12:29:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;backport patch for 0.94 updated.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/12576375/hbase-8174.patch&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/12576375/hbase-8174.patch&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13618917" author="yuzhihong@gmail.com" created="Mon, 1 Apr 2013 16:55:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Integrated to 0.94&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the patch, clockfly.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the reviews, Sergey, Lars and Anoop.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13618953" author="sershe" created="Mon, 1 Apr 2013 17:35:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;um, sorry to respond late, by &quot;still may not work&quot; above I meant that both will probably be necessary.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-8161&quot; title=&quot;setting blocking file count on table level doesn&amp;#39;t work&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-8161&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-8161&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; requires ability to add settings on table or CF, which 0.94 doesn&apos;t have (correct me if I&apos;m wrong).&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-5335&quot; title=&quot;Dynamic Schema Configurations&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-5335&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-5335&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; adds one of them and &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-7236&quot; title=&quot;add per-table/per-cf configuration via metadata&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-7236&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-7236&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; sub-jiras add both but much more intrusively. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13619192" author="hudson" created="Mon, 1 Apr 2013 21:26:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Integrated in HBase-0.94 #934 (See &lt;a href=&quot;https://builds.apache.org/job/HBase-0.94/934/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://builds.apache.org/job/HBase-0.94/934/&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;br/&gt;
